import React from "react"; import {Row, Col} from "react-bootstrap"; import "./index.css"; /** Card-like block for use in timelines * * Props: * - moment: date of the event * - title * - body: event text * - image: marker image src */ const TimelineItem = ({className, style, ...props}) => { return( {props.moment}

{props.title}

{props.body}

{props.moment} ) } export default TimelineItem;
